{"tid":2184891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提升台灣辨識度 公佈新版護照","createTime":"2020-09-02T02:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T02:34:31.000Z","uid":283070,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bc5450f223d76934228d5551e79034e27484e5","tid":2184891,"uid":283070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:08:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200902/27UXF74HDBERZC6FH2G5L6HVBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200902%2F27UXF74HDBERZC6FH2G5L6HVBA%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=6c3f34fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200902%2F27UXF74HDBERZC6FH2G5L6HVBA%2F&h=3e17a4ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200902/27UXF74HDBERZC6FH2G5L6HVBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n為了提升台灣在國際間的辨識度，行政院今（2日）發出通知，上午10點將舉行「新版護照封面」記者會，由行政院發言人丁怡銘主持，外交部長吳釗燮出席。據了解，新版護照封面的「中華民國」、「Republic of China」字樣都還在，但會新增凸顯台灣的圖示，增加對台灣的辨識度。<br />\n<br />\n立法院今年7月通過公決案，要求提高護照上「台灣」、「TAIWAN」辨識度，並請行政部門提出具體作法。當時立院也通過公決案要求華航飛機塗裝重新設計。<br />\n<br />\n希望香港嘅護照將來有一日都可以咁樣！"},{"pid":"c983aee44fced1189fda014e7d71f76bf551b5e3","tid":2184891,"uid":2054,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URsV9Ey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURsV9Ey.jpg&h=efe3b270&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fceb4f79b3682940ccef6009b2fe95213d73bf7","tid":2184891,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"香港嘅護照咪british passport囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8830e244f947b837c36ab16aa814369d46be12","tid":2184891,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-pe